### Test Payment Service Connection
GET https://localhost:7002/api/payments/test

### Get All Payments
GET https://localhost:7002/api/payments

### Get Payment by ID
GET https://localhost:7002/api/payments/1

### Get Payments by Order ID
GET https://localhost:7002/api/payments/order/1

### Create Payment (requires existing order)
POST https://localhost:7002/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "amount": 25.99,
  "status": "Pending",
  "paymentMethod": "Credit Card",
  "transactionId": "txn_123456789"
}

### Update Payment Status
PUT https://localhost:7002/api/payments/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Completed"
}
